  "section": "668",
  "title": "Unlawful Intent from Unlawful Act Presumption",
  "text": "An unlawful intent is presumed from the doing of an unlawful act. This presumption is inapplicable in a criminal action to establish the specific intent of the defendant where specific intent is an element of the crime charged.",
